# GeoResilience Hub — Phase 1 Implementation Plan

**Project:** GeoResilience Hub Website  
**Founders:** Sambus Geospatial & AcuGeospatial  
**Date:** May 11, 2026  
**Status:** Phase 1 — Approved for Implementation  

---

## 1. Project Overview

GeoResilience Hub is a professional geospatial consulting website for **two partners**:

| Partner | Brand | Role |
|---|---|---|
| Emmanuel Yerbo | **Sambus Geospatial** | GIS & Remote Sensing, Flood Mapping, GeoAI |
| Gifty Gyamera-Annor | **AcuGeospatial** | GIS Mapping, Land & Urban Planning, Data Support |

The site will serve as a **client-facing platform** to showcase services, display an interactive flood vulnerability map, provide pricing/contact information, and build credibility through testimonials.

> [!NOTE]
> All text content, images, and testimonials are **placeholders** for Phase 1. The client will supply real logos, photos, bios, and testimonial quotes in a later update pass.

