## 3. Design System

### Color Palette (Dark Mode Primary)

| Token | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `--bg-primary` | `#0f1117` | Page background |
| `--bg-secondary` | `#1a1d27` | Card/section backgrounds |
| `--bg-glass` | `rgba(26,29,39,0.7)` | Glassmorphism panels |
| `--accent-green` | `#2ecc71` | Primary accent, CTAs |
| `--accent-gold` | `#f0c040` | Highlights, ratings |
| `--text-primary` | `#e8e8e8` | Body text |
| `--text-secondary` | `#8b8fa3` | Muted text |
| `--risk-low` | `#27ae60` | Map: low risk |
| `--risk-medium` | `#f39c12` | Map: medium risk |
| `--risk-high` | `#e74c3c` | Map: high risk |

### Light Mode Toggle
- Full light mode palette as alternate CSS custom properties
- Toggle switch in navbar (sun/moon icon)
- User preference saved in `localStorage`

### Typography
- **Headings:** `'Outfit', sans-serif` (Google Fonts)
- **Body:** `'Inter', sans-serif` (Google Fonts)

### UI Principles
- Glassmorphism cards with `backdrop-filter: blur()`
- Subtle gradient borders on hover
- Micro-animations on scroll (fade-in, slide-up via Intersection Observer)
- Smooth page transitions
- Fully responsive (mobile-first breakpoints at 768px, 1024px, 1440px)

---

## 4. Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| Structure | HTML5 | Semantic, accessible |
| Styling | Vanilla CSS (custom properties) | Full control, no framework bloat |
| Logic | Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+) | Dark mode, animations, form handling |
| Maps | Google Earth Engine JS API (embedded) | Direct GEE app embed for flood map |
| Fonts | Google Fonts (Outfit, Inter) | Modern, premium typography |
| Icons | Lucide Icons (CDN) | Clean, consistent iconography |
| Hosting | GitHub Pages (initial) | Free, version-controlled |
| Forms | Formspree or EmailJS | Serverless contact form submission |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> No frameworks (React, Vue, etc.) needed for Phase 1. Pure HTML/CSS/JS keeps the site fast, simple to maintain, and easy for the client to update content.

