## 7. Time Estimate

### Detailed Breakdown

| Task | Description | Hours |
|---|---|---|
| **Design System Setup** | CSS custom properties, typography, color palette, dark/light mode toggle, base reset | 3 |
| **Navbar & Footer** | Responsive nav with mobile hamburger, dark mode switch, footer with contacts/socials | 2.5 |
| **Home Page** | Hero section, service cards, team teaser, stats counter, CTA sections, scroll animations | 5 |
| **About Page** | Partner profiles, certifications grid, "Who We Work With" section | 3 |
| **Services Page** | 3 service category cards with expandable details, sample images | 3.5 |
| **Interactive Map Page** | GEE App build (adapt existing flood code to ui.Map), embed iframe, info panel | 6 |
| **Testimonials Page** | Carousel/slider component, placeholder cards, star ratings | 2.5 |
| **Pricing Page** | 3-tier cards, FAQ accordion, "Custom Quote" CTA | 3 |
| **Contact Page** | Form with validation, Formspree/EmailJS integration, Google Maps embed | 3 |
| **Image Generation** | Generate all placeholder visuals (hero, services, team, testimonials) | 2 |
| **Responsive Polish** | Mobile/tablet breakpoints, touch interactions, cross-browser testing | 3 |
| **Dark/Light Mode** | Full theme toggle with localStorage persistence, all pages tested | 1.5 |
| **SEO & Meta** | Title tags, meta descriptions, Open Graph tags, semantic HTML audit | 1 |

### Summary

| Metric | Estimate |
|---|---|
| **Total Hours** | **38–48 hours** |
| **Working Days (6–8 hrs/day)** | **5–7 days** |
| **Calendar Days (realistic)** | **7–10 days** |

> [!TIP]
> The GEE Interactive Map is the single most complex component (~6 hours). If the existing GEE flood code is well-structured, this could come in closer to 4 hours. Everything else is standard web development.

### Suggested Build Order

```
Day 1 ──► Design system + Navbar/Footer + Home page structure
Day 2 ──► Home page polish + About page
Day 3 ──► Services page + Pricing page
Day 4 ──► Contact page + Testimonials page
Day 5 ──► GEE Interactive Map (build + embed)
Day 6 ──► Image generation + Responsive polish
Day 7 ──► Dark/light mode testing + SEO + Final QA
```

